{"title":"把手给我！","authors":["阿·恰奇"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"把手给我！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿尔巴尼亚　阿·恰奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把手给我！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！徐学惠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的手多么有力！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的姊妹，你从哪里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"获得这一切力量？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你感受到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有着什么样的朋友！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人把你的双手切断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是他们不能把你内心的火焰熄灭！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这火焰炽烈地燃烧着，燃烧着……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个朋友给你安装的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比真手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更加有力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我到过的所有地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我都听到人们呼唤着“苏联”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国的各个地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都呼唤着“苏联”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在整个世界上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都听到人们在呼唤着“苏联”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐学惠，我的姊妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应该永远记着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洛玛诺夫，用他给你的双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你啊，建设起未来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，也许我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——虽然我的头发已开始花白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将会坐上苏联的火箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到月宫去和嫦娥会见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐学惠，我的姊妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你做的真好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了共产主义，献出了自己的双手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！我多么渴望向你学习！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你真行！我的姊妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一条道路上前进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人会看到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是用这样的双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也会建设起共产主义！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1960，2，10　北京〔李宁来译，戈宝权校〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}